drm/amd/display: Add DCN3 OPTC

Add support for programming the DCN3 OPTC (Output Timing Controller)

HW Blocks:

    +--------+
    |  OPTC  |
    +--------+
        |
        v
    +--------+       +--------+
    |  DIO   |       |  DCCG  |
    +--------+       +--------+

